00:17:48.268 --> 00:17:51.188
para maamoy mo ang masarap at pinatuyo ng araw na pabango!

00:17:52.228 --> 00:17:53.748
Sige, hayaan mo akong tulungan ka.

00:17:53.788 --> 00:17:54.948
Okay, mahal.

00:17:55.203 --> 00:17:56.628
- Okay.
